										<div class="content newfont_family">
							<p><br /></p>
<p style=
'text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0; mso-pagination:widow-orphan'>
<span style='font-family: 宋体;'>最近网上流传着一篇文章，标题是“</span><span style=
'font-family: 宋体;'>突发！降价潮来袭，广州两天降<span>6</span>千<span>/</span>！武汉直降<span>8</span>千<span>/</span>！楼市风向大变”。该文章列举的例子有，</span><span style='font-family: 宋体;'>一线城市广州频频传出降价的消息！番禺大盘祈福缤纷汇几次推出促销房，<span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm; padding:0cm;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold'>从最高的<span>4.6</span>万<span>/</span>降到最低<span>3.6</span>万<span>/</span>，降幅超过<span>20%</span>。而</span>广州二手房从<span>2018</span>年下半年开始见顶回落，今年上半年又是量价齐跌，数据显示，<span>2019</span>年上半年，广州二手房成交量最高跌幅达到<span>32%</span>。</span></p>
<p style=
'text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0; mso-pagination:widow-orphan'>
<span style='font-family: 宋体;'>合肥庐阳地王原单价均是</span></p>
